            <div xml:id="what are heavy"> 
                <interpGrp type="poembox">
                    <interp ana="#form" type="heavy"></interp>
                    <interp ana="#tone" type="sea"></interp>
                    <interp ana="#topic" type="youth"></interp>
                </interpGrp>
                <lg> 
                    
                    
                    
           
                    <l>What are heavy? Sea-sand and sorrow;</l>
                    <l>  What are brief? Today and tomorrow;</l>
                    <l> What are frail? Spring blossoms and youth;</l>
                    <l>  What are deep? The ocean and truth.</l>
           
                    <l>Source: https://www.familyfriendpoems.com/poem/what-are-heavy-by-christina-rossetti</l>
                    
